{
  "texts": [
    "All experimental protocols were approved by the Ethics Committee of Northwestern and Central Switzerland (EKNZ).",
    "This project was done under the regulatory framework for Human Research ACT in Switzerland.",
    "After revision, the EKNZ issued a waiver statement (declaration of no objection: AO_2021-00045) declaring that informed consent was not needed for experts.",
    "However, informed consent was verbally obtained from all subjects and audio-recorded at the beginning of each interview.",
    "Participants recruitmentTo be eligible for recruitment, AI experts had to have experience working with or developing AI for healthcare, allowing us to explore the views of various professional backgrounds."
  ]
}